title: Necklace, Initial Letter F, Stainless Steel
description: A great jewellery piece that has both - fashionable style and a personal touch. The pendant is made sophisticatedly and has a very high quality. The stainless steel plate is well finished and the shape of letter F is lasered out. The pendant looks chic and eyecatching. Both, the carabiner clasp and the closing ring are made of stainless steel as well. The black cord is 2mm thick and looks very chic together with this pendant. The necklace is suitable for women as well as for men with a great taste of fashion.
abe-description: Anhänger, Karabiner und Ring aus Edelstahl - Stainless Steel, an 2mm Gummi schwarz, als Einzelstück gefertigt
